column2: SELECT    H.recno, H.RAJ2#, H.DEJ2#, H.z, H.plate, H.mjd, H.fiber,    n.objid, n.distance,     p.ra AS pra, p.dec AS pdec, p.modelmag_r, p.modelmag_g,    s.specobjid, s.bestobjid, s.z as sz, s.plate AS splate, s.mjd AS smjd, s.fiberid AS sfiberid,    pz.z as photoz,    sm.mstellar_median FROM MyDB.Heckman AS H    OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(H.RAJ2#, H.DEJ2#, #) AS n    LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON n.objid=p.objid    LEFT JOIN SpecObj as s ON n.objid=s.bestobjid   LEFT JOIN Photoz as pz ON n.objid=pz.objid   LEFT JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# as sm ON s.specobjid=sm.specobjid INTO MyDB.HeckmanDR1# ORDER BY H.recno
